Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: radp-vagrant-framework
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash, coreutils, ruby, radp-bash-framework
Description: YAML-driven framework for managing multi-machine Vagrant environments.
 radp-vagrant-framework provides declarative configuration for VM clusters,
 networks, storage, and provisioning through a modular Ruby architecture.
 It supports configuration inheritance, builtin provisions and triggers,
 and plugin management for Vagrant environments.
